## Enable Direct Management API via ARM template

```json
{
    "type": "Microsoft.ApiManagement/service/tenant",
    "apiVersion": "2020-06-01-preview",
    "name": "[concat(parameters('Apim.Name'), '/access')]",
    "dependsOn": [
        "[resourceId('Microsoft.ApiManagement/service', parameters('Apim.Name'))]"
    ],
    "properties": {
        "enabled": true
    }
}
```

## Retrieve identifiers using Powershell

```pwsh
$apimContext = New-AzApiManagementContext -resourceGroupName <rg-name> -serviceName <apim-name>
Get-AzApiManagementTenantAccess -context $apimContext
```
